Description:
As you go around the tower you see a man with a wooden sword practicing some movements, when you approach he speaks to you:

"Hello adventurers, perhaps you are interested in some combat training? I can teach one of you my special defensive move for 200g, if you all want to learn it, it will cost you 1000g.

I used to train young soldiers in this tower, but since the war ended I am out of work and short of money."
DescriptionAction: This seems like an opportunity to learn something new.
